data.description: Discover the perfect 3-bed, 2-bath retreat with a master on the main floor. This doesn't miss a check box with an attached 2 car garage. Immerse yourself in the airy, sunlit spaces beneath towering vaulted ceilings. A welcoming ambiance of space as soon as you enter the front door. Upstairs, find your sanctuary on a walkout deck and a cozy entertainment haven.  Outside, your blank canvas yard awaits your creative touch. Centrally located and in a cul-de-sac, you're steps away from picturesque riverfront trails. Welcome home to a world of possibilities!
